categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: This Zabrak male was a Knight who served the Jedi Order during the waning years of the Galactic Republic. As the Clone Wars between the Republic and the Separatists was drawing to an end and Supreme Chancellor Palpatine issuing Order 66 across the galaxy, he was inside the Jedi Temple's library when he witnessed Anakin Skywalker enter with two clone troopers. He watched in horror when Skywalker executed Jedi Master Jocasta Nu. Along with other Jedi in the room, he tried to avenge Nu's death, but was slain by Vader which led to the beginning of the Great Jedi Purge.
